    <text>
        <body>
                <div1>
                        <lb ed="I" n="0062a01"/>正光五年歲次甲辰七月己酉朔十五日<note n="0062001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30495;＝癸【中研院】</note><app n="0062001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">癸</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30495;</rdg></app>亥。
                        <lb ed="I" n="0062a02"/>雍州北地三原縣仇臣生。值遇上世。信心三寶。
                        <lb ed="I" n="0062a03"/>造石像一<note n="0062002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30496;＝區【中研院】</note><app n="0062002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">區</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30496;</rdg></app>。上為皇帝陛下。州郡令長。七世父 
                        <lb ed="I" n="0062a04"/>母。願上生天上。值遇諸佛。下隧人間。侯王長者
                        <lb ed="I" n="0062a05"/>之家。現世之報。延年益壽。子孫興隆。<note n="0062003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30355;＝所【中研院】</note><app n="0062003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30355;</rdg></app>願如<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">斯</unclear>
                        <lb ed="I" n="0062a06"/>夫信欲稱善者。非至德不顯其功。欲游嵩岳者。
                        <lb ed="I" n="0062a07"/>非空寂<note n="0062004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30478;＝亦【中研院】</note><app n="0062004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">亦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30478;</rdg></app>不達其<note n="0062005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30355;＝所【中研院】</note><app n="0062005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30355;</rdg></app>。昔太子絕思於龍<note n="0062006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30497;＝華【中研院】</note><app n="0062006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">華</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30497;</rdg></app>。身<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">體</unclear>
                        <lb ed="I" n="0062a08"/>如來之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">願</unclear>。月<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">辰</unclear>叩白駒而脩禮。<note n="0062007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30478;＝亦【中研院】</note><app n="0062007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">亦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30478;</rdg></app>蒙神道之助。
                        <lb ed="I" n="0062a09"/>是以積善成道。累<note n="0062008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30498;＝惡【中研院】</note><app n="0062008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">惡</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30498;</rdg></app><note n="0062009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30499;＝滅【中研院】</note><app n="0062009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">滅</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30499;</rdg></app>身。宜斑經藉。流芳來葉。
                        <lb ed="I" n="0062a10"/>不敢多進。　　親祖仇收　忘父仇進興
                        <lb ed="I" n="0062a11"/>　　　　　　　　　　　忘叔仇<note n="0062010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30500;＝歸【中研院】</note><app n="0062010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">歸</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30500;</rdg></app>興
                </div1>
